<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-6770] camel-resltet - Restlet producer problem after recent upgrade</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-6770</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After Restlet 2.1.4 upgrade we have a problem with this test in tests/camel-itest&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;mvn test -Dtest=RestletDomainServiceTest&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It looks like the 2nd restlet call takes a long time and doesn&apos;t signal back when its done.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also we should make it easier to configure a connection / request timeout as well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
